57
00:06:03,096 --> 00:06:04,996
<i>Guía de París para amantes.</i>

58
00:06:07,533 --> 00:06:08,557
<i>Ah. Guía para amantes de la comida.</i>

59
00:06:08,634 --> 00:06:11,865
